(firstQuint)Automated Telephone Reminder for Colonoscopy.

 Randomized trial of automated reminders with bowel prep instructions and encouraging clear fluid ingestion.

 The phone calls will occur 48-96 hours prior to the scheduled colonoscopy.

 All patients undergoing outpatient colonoscopy and prescribed sodium picosulfate plus magnesium citrate will be eligible for enrollment.

